name: Token of Gratitude
description:
This is a utility token, 1 edition will be given to all collectors for every 5 different pieces you collect.

You can burn 1 edition of this token and trade it with my future work that is still available on primary

Thank you for all the support you’ve given so far. I know I’ve said this multiples time already, but I’m truly grateful for all you’ve done for me :)

1080 X 2048
